				<blockquote>I used Get_Native.com to sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Nulla veritatis, facilis quisquam labore doloremque laborum quia consequatur consequuntur officia veniam hic praesentium fuga numquam nemo repellat, quam dignissimos debitis a? <span clas="quote_authors">- Paul (19)</span></blockquote>
				<p>Still not convinced we're legit? <%= link_to "Read more reviews" %></p>
				
			</div> <!-- col-sm-6 -->

		</div> <!-- row -->
	  
</div> <!-- users_add sign_up container -->
